00:33:02.697 --> 00:33:05.030
Though this is a perfectly
legitimate thing to calculate

00:33:05.030 --> 00:33:09.880
and we know how to do it, or
McQuarrie knows how to do it.

00:33:09.880 --> 00:33:11.500
And you don't
really need to worry

00:33:11.500 --> 00:33:14.830
about doing these
integrals because this

00:33:14.830 --> 00:33:18.280
is at such a low-level
approximation,

00:33:18.280 --> 00:33:21.100
