00:33:21.100 --> 00:33:24.010
how to approach these problems.

00:33:24.010 --> 00:33:26.350
But we can still
do these integrals.

00:33:26.350 --> 00:33:27.600
And it's useful.

00:33:27.600 --> 00:33:29.970
And so what do you get?

00:33:29.970 --> 00:33:33.370
Well, you get minus
